{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2541660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为他们在利用科技、金融、军师方面的优势剥削我们。。。", "timestamp": 1631987045, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541669, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541660, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 经典昂撒，让我猜猜我每天是被美的剥削的多点还是十七家剥削的多点", "timestamp": 1631987107, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541671, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个“他们”就很有意思", "timestamp": 1631987119, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我的看法：因为我国不需要中层，有铁拳在，我国只需要加大力度剥削中层，顶层取九分，剩下一分用来照顾底层的稳定，维持在饿不死的状态；底层奋斗爬到中层的全部砍下去，空出位置让新的底层爬上来，然后再砍下去，循环往复", "timestamp": 1631987342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541712, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541690, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 反正中层没胆子，底层没动力，不需要西方那一套纺锤形社会，只需要特色的图钉形社会", "timestamp": 1631987634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先A说的问题是存在的，我国GDP总量是实实在在的低（相对14亿人口），我国的确需要高端产业来提高GDP的数量和质量；B说的也有一定道理，我国基尼系数世界前列，既得利益者地位太巩固。", "timestamp": 1631987730, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过我觉得还是要提高总量，你蛋糕不做大，再怎么分配也得饿死；蛋糕做大以后才有分配的空间。", "timestamp": 1631987859, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541733, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "发展程度确实影响很大啊，单论中产的物质生活，我国 GDP 上来后这些年中层过得比二三十年前中层好多了，没有疑义吧", "timestamp": 1631987915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541750, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541671, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 国家综合科技金融实力反映在人民生活上就是百姓生活。", "timestamp": 1631988157, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "然而少数人阶乘增长，多数人线性增长，被窃取的比例是不是更多了呢？", "timestamp": 1631988184, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541757, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "更别说现在消费增长乏力，所有人都被捆绑在房地产上，怕不是要变成对数了", "timestamp": 1631988265, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541762, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541690, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 第一句“因为我国不需要中层”我直接绷不住了。", "timestamp": 1631988363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541728, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 蛋糕已经很大了，该解决分配问题了", "timestamp": 1631988420, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "年轻人也在用生育率投票了，不解决分配问题，战车还能开多久？", "timestamp": 1631988422, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541770, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541728, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不解决分配还剩多少人接着做啊", "timestamp": 1631988490, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541773, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541717, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 洞主的问题是中国中产和美国中产比，那么就算bob口中的中国资本家再剥削，那也比美国资本家的剥削好些。", "timestamp": 1631988552, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541777, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541717, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不是说不该解决分配问题，而是分配问题比烂方面咱们又不输老美", "timestamp": 1631988622, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541780, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#政治相关", "timestamp": 1631988638, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541782, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实除了互联网通信房地产之外，我国其他产业发展真的非常差…比如生物医药、电路芯片、精密器械、化学化工、光学…我国真的很需要高新技术产业，但这些产业发展受到美国压制也是实打实的", "timestamp": 1631988641, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541766, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 分配问题在莓果不突出的原因是因为他们蛋糕比我们大得多，而不是因为他们的分配问题没我们的严重。", "timestamp": 1631988686, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541789, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541777, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对啊，所以蛋糕先做大才是问题…很多人不会已经飘了吧，忘记我们还是个发展中国家吗？", "timestamp": 1631988695, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541796, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541777, "tag": null, "text": "就目前这个人均GDP…你看看世界上这个人均GDP的国家，哪个国家人民生活幸福…", "timestamp": 1631988798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541789, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 两手一起抓吧，又不冲突。", "timestamp": 1631988817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541798, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541782, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 没办法，毕竟这种东西也不是一天两天能搞出来的更何况市场经济搞了这么久，还指望国家一声令下就一票人呕心沥血为国捐躯，几年赶超世界水平也太离谱了", "timestamp": 1631988825, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541804, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要是能保证再整出一个00～20年的互联网这样的通道，ok我没意见，然而现在大多数人都已经看到（比如树洞的讨论），连这最后一个通道都要关闭堵死了", "timestamp": 1631988917, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541819, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541804, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 下一个通道还是得期待新兴技术产业啊…也许是量子计算什么的？我不清楚，但是我知道没有高新技术，知识分子的生活水平很难有质的提高。", "timestamp": 1631989058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541822, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？我哪里说到言论自由了", "timestamp": 1631989108, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541824, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541822, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我的，我急了看错了。", "timestamp": 1631989141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541822, "tag": null, "text": "我不是在说现在蛋糕分不好又做不大吗？你别撤回啊", "timestamp": 1631989150, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541831, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541825, "tag": null, "text": "睡了", "timestamp": 1631989238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541825, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 首先，善用回复。\n很简单的道理，分不好的问题中美都有，而且强烈怀疑美国更严重。\n所以不能说中国中产生活的没有美国中产好是因为蛋糕没分好。", "timestamp": 1631989271, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541836, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541825, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 至于为什么中国的蛋糕没有美国的大——历史原因，而且也确实在被压制咯。", "timestamp": 1631989321, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541825, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: bob选择性回复我的言论真的是很有趣呢。", "timestamp": 1631989346, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541843, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541819, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 造舰的作用不是摆脱美国的压制和剥削，而是为了去剥削其他国家（）", "timestamp": 1631989446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544701, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为中国人怕死，不愿意闹事，你可以说国外资本家是靠剥削广大第三世界国家人民的，但是国外工人福利绝对是他们自己工人运动的结果。", "timestamp": 1632039113, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2548825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": 2541765, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 真的够大了吗，相同水平人均gdp的哪个国家过上好日子了？", "timestamp": 1632070913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2739413, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 485403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "。", "timestamp": 1634360127, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 14, "pid": 485403, "reply": 37, "tag": null, "text": "为什么我国中产百姓生活得没有美国中产好？？", "timestamp": 1631986924, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1634360129, "url": "", "vote": {}}}